question: Jenny Kim has been crowned Miss Supranational 2017. She hails from which country?
explanation: Jenny Kim, a South Korean beauty pageant titleholder, has been crowned Miss Supranational 2017 in Krynica-Zdroj, Poland on December 1, 2017. She was crowned by the very beautiful Miss Supranational 2016 \"Srinidhi Ramesh Shetty\" of India. Altogether 65 contestants from across the globe participated at the prestigious pageant with Jenny Kim emerging victorious.
